parts.part: Lady D. Beauclerc Mr Mrs Vesey

relation.text: went to Courteen Hall 8 th . June
s . 10 Return 'd home 28 Went to Thames Ditton 7 th July
did not see him Monday June 23
had written upon friendship 24 th . June 1783
exceeded my ideas -- ye . grand ure eur & beauty of ye Architectu re & proportions -- ye . Church was 40 years
June 1783 -- at 11 my Uncle Frederick for an hour -- Mrs. Newton -- Mrs . & Miſs Hamilton Mrs H brought
went to bed past 12 Mrs- Scott all day 26 -- June 1783
went together in the Coach to Mrs Garricks at Hampton we had much pleasant converse in ye Coach Miſs Hamilton Clarges Street Satry June 28
1783 Clarges Street Miſs A Clarke & I breakfasted
came away Thames Ditton near Thurston upon Thames Sunday
'd to me of her Son his being in her power & c & c Thames Ditton July 1
cost L 10-000 -- it had been finish 'd above 4 years
netted . & c & c Thames Ditton July 2
follow 'd this emploment for her livelihood since she was 9 Years
Sunday if ye . Glovers who was not well was better or if Lord Warwick came up
tomorrow . had a very agreeable ride to Thames Ditton Mr . communicated
resign 'd the appartments she had in ye Castle for 15 Years
went to bed Thames Ditton July 4
read some of ye . Criticisms in ye . different Reviews for ye . last Month
'd upon Mrs. W . Blair & c Thames Ditton July 5
July Thames Ditton . I did not go
Keep lively Conversation -- did not separate till past 12 oClock . Monday
went to her Sons Mrs. H . into Suſsex Yesterday
sent me a very fine plate of fruit Pine apple & c & c 8th July
read some of Youngs Satires & c & c x 9 th July 1783
July 10 th . ye . Veseys & I went
came for a few Min : to me in my dreſsing Room . July 11
Saturday -- M r Stan Bell & I came
overturn of a Coach last Year
brought to bed of a girl Saturday 12 July 1783
talk 'd of Mrs. Carter . & c -- Sunday 13 July 1783
was brought to bed a week ago
3 Weeks to Sunning hill to my Uncle Frederick s
had enquired after me when she was last week
had not gone away before 5 oClock June 22
